      MANAGING WORKPLACE VIOLENCE

      CIVIL is a coordinated NIH resource which strives to attain its vision
      of: "An NIH Work Environment Free of Acts and Threats of Violence".

      VIOLENT SITUATIONS:

        IMMEDIATE DANGER:



   Dial 911, Bethesda campus Dial 9-911, other NIH offices

      Call CIVIL if:

         You need help assessing the potential seriousness of a threatening
        situation;

         You are experiencing a threatening situation at work and need
        intervention from trained staff;

         You become aware of a workplace situation involving intimidating,
        harassing, or other unproductive/dangerous behaviors and need
        consultation; or

         A situation involving threats or aggressive acts already has
        occurred and you need assistance managing the aftermath and its
        effect on staff; or

         You need help in addressing your own aggressive reactions to a
        workplace situation.
        __________________________________________________________________

      We welcome your comments. Please send your comments to
   SteinbeS@od.nih.gov
